Package juisynth.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ADSRPanel
    ADSRPanel is a class extending JPanel containing the GUI elements relevant to an ADSR envelope.
    GUI
    The main class of the GUI, instantiating the panels and listeners contained in the frame.
    OperatorPanel
    OperatorPanel is a class extending JPanel containing the GUI elements relevant to an Operator.
    OscillatorOptionsPanel
    OscillatorOptionsPanel is a class extending JPanel containing the GUI elements relevant to an Oscillator.
    PlayerPanel
    PlayerPanel is a class extending JPanel containing the GUI elements relevant to an Player.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ADSRParameter
    Enumerator for the parameters modified by GUI elements relating to ADSR.
    OperatorMode
    Enumerator for the boolean parameters modified by GUI elements relating to Operator.
    OperatorParameter
    Enumerator for the floating point parameters modified by GUI elements relating to ADSR.
    PlayerMode
    Enumerator for the methods triggered by GUI elements relating to Player.
